  <entry>
    <title>Hexo and minos</title>
    <link href="/2023/05/23/CS/Hexo-and-minos/"/>
    <url>/2023/05/23/CS/Hexo-and-minos/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="/2023/05/23/CS/Hexo-and-minos/godfather.png"><br>The image is write as <code>![](/2023/05/23/CS/Hexo-and-minos/godfather.png)</code></p><h2 id="About-Hexo"><a href="#About-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="About Hexo"></a>About Hexo</h2><p>21.5.23, 我建立了我的第一个（正式的）博客，用的是Github + Hexo. 开头很顺利，今天换主题的时候有些小bug。在此记录过程，方便以后迁移。</p><ul><li><p><code>install node.js, git, hexo</code></p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ npm i hexo-cli -g<br>$ hexo -v <span class="hljs-comment"># to check for successful installation</span><br>$ hexo init &lt;<span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span> name&gt;<br>$ npm install ...<br>$ hexo g <span class="hljs-comment"># generate static web page</span><br>$ hexo s <span class="hljs-comment"># start local serve to preview, ctrl + click the url to open it</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><code>connect your github</code></p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;zz2summer&quot;</span> <br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;xxxxx@163.com&quot;</span><br>ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;summer2zz@163.com&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  open github, click settings &gt; SSH and GPG keys, create a new ssh key.</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  copy the output to the new ssh key.</p></li><li><p><code>modify blog/_config.yml</code><br>  open _config.yml, change the last line:</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">deploy:<br><span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>: git<br>repository: git@...<br>branch: main<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="Write-new-blog"><a href="#Write-new-blog" class="headerlink" title="Write new blog"></a>Write new blog</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ npm i hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment"># install a new plugin</span><br>$ hexo new post <span class="hljs-string">&quot;title&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># create a new blog</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Then open blog&#x2F;source&#x2F;_posts, there will be a new file named <code>title.md</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo g -d <span class="hljs-comment"># generate the web page and push new change to github</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>If needed to upload images, modify _config.yml:<br><code>post_assert_folder: true</code></p><h2 id="Delete-blog"><a href="#Delete-blog" class="headerlink" title="Delete blog"></a>Delete blog</h2><p>delete blog&#x2F;source&#x2F;_posts&#x2F;delete.md, and run <code>hexo d -g</code></p><h2 id="Customize-home-page"><a href="#Customize-home-page" class="headerlink" title="Customize home page"></a>Customize home page</h2><p>Creating an index.md file in the blog&#x2F;source folder. Then change blog&#x2F;_config.yml:</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yml"><span class="hljs-attr">index_generator:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-comment">#path: &#x27;&#x27;  # DELETE</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">path:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/blog&#x27;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
